description:
UnrealProfileThemes

Allows you to fake having profile colors by encoding them into your bio, anyone with this plugin or the FakeProfileColors plugin on vencord can see these colors

To use just select the colors you want then click copy 3y3 and paste the value anywhere in your bio. If you wish to hide the missing character icons then enable "Strip Missing Letters" in settings

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Futuremappermydud/Emnity-UnrealProfileThemes/main/dist/UnrealProfileThemes.js
Source: https://github.com/Futuremappermydud/Emnity-UnrealProfileThemes
